{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"19ca2c67ad","title":"毛泽东主席会见巴基斯坦总理布托谈话记录","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5d81e4d82a","index":0,"year":1976,"month":5,"day":27,"articleId":"19ca2c67ad"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"090f4bd003","type":"title","text":"毛泽东主席会见巴基斯坦总理布托谈话记录（未经毛主席审阅）","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"19ca2c67ad"},{"id":"bb5de4198f","type":"paragraph","text":"时  间：1976年5月27日晚8时35分至8时45分","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"19ca2c67ad"},{"id":"31df896e7e","type":"paragraph","text":"地  点：中南海","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"19ca2c67ad"},{"id":"993794712d","type":"paragraph","text":"参加人：巴方——国防和外交国务部长阿齐兹·艾哈迈德","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"19ca2c67ad"},{"id":"b2ded6ac26","type":"paragraph","text":"中方——华国锋","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"19ca2c67ad"},{"id":"66f632f191","type":"paragraph","text":"翻  译：冀朝铸","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"19ca2c67ad"},{"id":"2b5f476513","type":"paragraph","text":"记  录：张铁根","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"19ca2c67ad"},{"id":"510d6fea16","type":"paragraph","text":"（毛主席高兴地同布托总理握手）","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"19ca2c67ad"},{"id":"f6b6fbddd4","type":"paragraph","text":"佐·阿·布托总理（以下简称布托）：我非常高兴见到毛主席。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"19ca2c67ad"},{"id":"20986263a6","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：欢迎你。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"19ca2c67ad"},{"id":"debaff42f9","type":"paragraph","text":"（毛主席与布托夫人握手）","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"19ca2c67ad"},{"id":"9995d29667","type":"paragraph","text":"布托夫人：我见到主席感到非常荣幸","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"19ca2c67ad"},{"id":"33dda3beb5","type":"paragraph","text":"（毛主席与阿齐兹·艾哈迈德部长握手。布托夫人向毛主席告辞，毛主席请布托总理和阿齐兹·艾哈迈德部长入座。）","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"19ca2c67ad"},{"id":"16e21c949e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：你好吗？","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"19ca2c67ad"},{"id":"e33bbef1c8","type":"paragraph","text":"布托：我很好，谢谢你，主席。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"19ca2c67ad"},{"id":"d1e2a9ef6b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：我不大好，（指腿）腿不大好，讲话也不大好。（指布托总理和华总理）你们谈得怎么样?","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"19ca2c67ad"},{"id":"92c53ac450","type":"paragraph","text":"布托：我们的讨论进行得非常好。我们已经讨论过两次了，我们讨论了许多问题。我们的观点基本上都是一致的。","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"19ca2c67ad"},{"id":"9bd42dda73","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：那很好。","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"19ca2c67ad"},{"id":"e6998a8e1a","type":"paragraph","text":"布托：我们还将进一步讨论。在我谈下去以前，我想先说一下，毛主席抽出时间来接见我和我的外长，这使我非常感动。我记和很清楚，1963年我来北京签订边界协定的时候，主席就接见了我，以后我又有幸多次见到主席。祝毛主席健康长寿。","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"19ca2c67ad"},{"id":"74616ede77","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席。我不好。","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"19ca2c67ad"},{"id":"44e91602fc","type":"paragraph","text":"布托：但是主席创造了伟大的历史。主席高举着人民革命斗争的旗帜。","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"19ca2c67ad"},{"id":"815b48844a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：没有做出多少成绩。你们巴基斯坦搞得好吗？","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"19ca2c67ad"},{"id":"437a1562e1","type":"paragraph","text":"布托：我们国内的情况很好。自从我担任总理职务4年以来，我们取得了很大的进步，我们正在加强国内的团结。由于友好国家，特别是中国对我们的友好援助，使我们能够取得很大的进展。我特此表示感谢。这是因为我们同中国之间有了如此坚定的友谊。","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"19ca2c67ad"},{"id":"a8088bf190","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：好啊。","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"19ca2c67ad"},{"id":"d61ab346f9","type":"paragraph","text":"布托：我可以向你保证，我们永远不会让苏联的霸权主义统治巴基斯坦。虽然他们对我们的压力很大，但是，在中国的支持下，我们顶住了压力。我们的人民团结一致进行抵抗。苏联很想得到我们的暖洋水域，但是我们是不会让他们得逞的。他们是来自一个寒冷地带，我们怎么能够让它到暖洋地方来呢？","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"19ca2c67ad"},{"id":"abe39faa46","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：就是嘛！","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"19ca2c67ad"},{"id":"7d8c42bde3","type":"paragraph","text":"（用手指指华总理和布托总理）你们去谈吧。","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"19ca2c67ad"},{"id":"da294d77ab","type":"paragraph","text":"华总理：好。有些事情布托总理就和我谈了。有些事情需要请示主席，我再请示。今天是不是就谈到这里。","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"19ca2c67ad"},{"id":"be8633df85","type":"paragraph","text":"（布托总理和阿齐兹·艾哈迈德部长起身告辞，毛主席与外宾握手告别。）","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"19ca2c67ad"},{"id":"9e8abaaf3c","type":"paragraph","text":"布托：非常感谢你。","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"19ca2c67ad"}],"page":{"id":"a34e694e57","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"19ca2c67ad","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}